column5: IMMP they will also be able to discover a lifesaving drug but always red will make it close they suck at those who speculate here

IMMP As such this new patent provides patent protection in Europe for a range of novel and highly relevant chemoimmunotherapies featuring efti that may be pursued in the futureThe patent expiry date is 19 December 2034

IMMP Dr Frédéric Triebel Immutep CSO and CMO commented This new patent is important because platinumbased chemotherapy agents and topoisomerase I inhibitors continue to be commonly used forms of chemotherapy In addition the past couple of years has seen for the first time the marketing approval and adoption of first or second line combinations of chemotherapy and active immunotherapies for the treatment of advanced solid tumors
IMMP it should have flown today Wtf

IMMP The patent is a critical part of the business plan Efti is being set up to be a companion to many approved and clinical stage therapies I wouldnt expect the market to care but in the big picture its about helping as many patients as possible live a longer life As a simple subcutaneous shot the robust immune response from efti is an ideal companion for oncologist to improve response
IMMP good news and it comes down were at the casino
